{"title":"Git Branch(分支)","date":"2018-08-09T18:46:00.000Z","link":"post/188","categories":["Git"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:04:37.657Z","content":"<ol>\n<li><p>查看分支</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git branch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>创建分支</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git branch &lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>切换分支</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git checkout &lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><p>创建 + 切换分支</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git checkout -b &lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>合并某分支到 当前分支上</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// fast forward 合并模式</span><br><span class=\"line\">git merge &lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 普通合并模式</span><br><span class=\"line\">git merge --no-ff -m &apos;some comments&apos; dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>删除分支</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git branch -d &lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 强行删除一个没有被合并过的分支</span><br><span class=\"line\">git branch -D &lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>查看合并分支情况</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git log --graph --pretty=oneline --abbrev-commit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>stash</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 当前工作副本临时保存</span><br><span class=\"line\">git stash</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 所有 stash 的工作副本</span><br><span class=\"line\">git stash list</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 恢复工作副本(并不删除)</span><br><span class=\"line\">git stash apply stash@&#123;0&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 删除工作副本</span><br><span class=\"line\">git stash grop stash@&#123;0&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 恢复最近一次的工作副本, 并且删除该副本</span><br><span class=\"line\">git stash pop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>与远程服务器</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 查看远程服务器信息</span><br><span class=\"line\">git remote -v</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 将本地分支推送到远程服务器(本地不推送到远程服务器,别人看不到)</span><br><span class=\"line\">// (如果失败可以先 git pull 从服务器上拉取新的提交)</span><br><span class=\"line\">git push origin local-branch:remote-branch</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 创建本地和远程对应的分支</span><br><span class=\"line\">// (两者名称最好一直)</span><br><span class=\"line\">git checkout -b &lt;branch-name&gt; origin/&lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 建立本地分支与远程分支的关联</span><br><span class=\"line\">git branch --set-upstream &lt;branch-name&gt; origin/&lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 从远程分支抓取</span><br><span class=\"line\">git pull</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">//提交远程分支</span><br><span class=\"line\"> git push --set-upstream origin develop3.0.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"order by 多字段排序","link":"post/192"},"next":{"title":"PLSQL添加新的链接数据库（DBLINK方式）","link":"post/179"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/188/"}